mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: SPECIAL FEATURES "What's Being Danced?", "Square Dance Associations: The Dancer's Associations", "What'll Be Doing in Denver", "Energy Incorporated - That's Eb Jenkins", "Homes for Square Dancing, Part II", "Survey of Round Dancing", "Caller Round Up", and "Hints on Developing "Caller Personality"". This edition also includes the the regular features entitled "Square Dance Date Book", "As I See It", "Style Series: Red Hot", "Chuck Jones' Note Book", "Round the Outside Ring", "Paging the Roundancers: Elmer and Rosemarie Elias", "Caller of the Month: Selmer Hovland", "From the Floor", "On the Record", and "Ladies on the Square: Square Dance Purses".
